videos.description: Mitchell Guadagni is picked off on Toledo's opening drive by Buffalo's Aapri Washington.
videos.headline: Toledo's Guadagni throws INT on opening drive

videos.description: Buffalo's Tyree Jackson is hit on the blindside and Toledo's Jamal Hines comes up with the interception at the line of scrimmage.
videos.headline: Rockets' defense comes up with big INT

videos.description: Bryant Koback bursts through the middle for a 70-yard rushing touchdown for the Rockets.
videos.headline: Koback breaks out for 70-yard TD

videos.description: Charlie Jones lays out to grab the 44-yard pass from Tyree Jackson.
videos.headline: Buffalo WR dives for 44-yard reception

videos.description: Justin Clark snatches the deep pass from Buffalo's Tyree Jackson for a big-time interception for the Toledo defense.
videos.headline: Toledo defense secures second INT of day

videos.description: Eli Peters comes in and drops a dime to Diontae Johnson, who takes it all the way for an 80-yard Toledo touchdown.
videos.headline: Toledo QB Peters tosses 80-yard TD pass

videos.description: Buffalo regains possession by forcing a fumble after Tyree Jackson's pass was intercepted moments before.
videos.headline: Buffalo retains possession after improbable turnover sequence

videos.description: Tyree Jackson throws a strike up the middle to Anthony Johnson who takes it in for a 32-yard Buffalo touchdown.
videos.headline: Jackson connects with Johnson to draw Buffalo even

videos.description: Eli Peters' pass is picked off by Brandon Williams as the wind picks up early in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Peters throws crucial Toledo INT

videos.description: Jaret Patterson gives Buffalo its first lead of the day with a 6-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Buffalo takes the lead with Patterson TD

videos.description: Jaret Patterson breaks out for a 25-yard touchdown run to put Buffalo up over Toledo 31-17.
videos.headline: Patterson scores second rushing TD
